# Ubuntu
1. bump verion in DEBIAN/control
2. copy DEBIAN directory into deb
3. create docs dir: deb/usr/share/doc/pianobar-version/
4. create binary dir deb/usr/bin/
5. compile and copy pianobar executable into deb/usr/bin/
6. gzip COPYING and README into docs dir
7. copy contrib into docs dir
8. dpkg -b ./deb pianobar-version-i386.deb
